l></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Um&nbsp;<strong>elemento</strong> <strong>HTML <code>&lt;label&gt;</code> </strong>representa uma legenda para um item em uma interface de usuário. Ele&nbsp;pode estar associado&nbsp;com um elemento de controle, colocando este&nbsp;dentro do elemento&nbsp;<code>label</code>, ou usando o atributo&nbsp;<code>for</code>. Tal controle é chamado o <em>controle etiquetado</em> do elemento etiqueta. Um input pode ser associado a diversas etiquetas (&lt;label&gt;s).</p>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">As categorias de conteúdo</a></dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Flow content</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#interactive_content\">interactive content</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#form-associated_content\">form-associated element</a>, palpable content.</li>\n <li><dfn>conteúdo permitido</dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\">Phrasing content</a>, mas há elementos do rótulo descendente. Nenhum outro do que o controle rotulado elementos labelable são permitidos.</li>\n <li><dfn>Tag omissão</dfn> None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</li>\n <li><dfn><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\">Elementos pai permitidas</span></dfn> Qualquer elemento que aceita <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>DOM interface</dfn> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLLabelElement\"><code>HTMLLabelElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A tecla de atalho para acessar este elemento a partir do teclado.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"accesskey\"><a id=\"attr-accesskey\" href=\"#attr-accesskey\"><b><code>accesskey</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML 4</a></span> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>A tecla de atalho para acessar este elemento a partir do teclado.</dd>\n <dt id=\"for\"><a id=\"attr-for\" href=\"#attr-for\"><b><code>for</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>O ID de um elemento de formulário relacionados com labelable no mesmo documento como o elemento label. O primeiro elemento tal no documento com uma ID correspondente ao valor do atributo é o controle marcado for este elemento etiqueta.\n <div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><strong>Nota: </strong>Um elemento etiqueta pode ter tanto um for o atributo e um elemento de controlo continham, enquanto os pontos de atributo para o elemento de controlo contido.</span></div>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"form\"><a id=\"attr-form\" href=\"#attr-form\"><b><code>form</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>\n <div class=\"almost_half_cell\" id=\"gt-res-content\">\n <div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"zoom: 1;\" id=\"sect2\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\">O elemento de forma que o elemento label está associado a (seu proprietário formulário). O valor do atributo deve ser uma identificação de um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a> elemento no mesmo documento. Se este atributo não for especificado, este elemento &lt;label&gt; deve ser um descendente de uma <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a> elemento. Este atributo permite que você coloque elementos do rótulo em qualquer lugar dentro de um documento, e não apenas como descendentes de seus elementos de formulário.</span></div>\n </div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo_simples_de_label","title":"Exemplo simples de label","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\" style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans',sans-serif; line-height: 23.3333px;\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Click me <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>User<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Name<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Exemplo simples de label\" id=\"frame_simple_label_example\" width=\"200\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label/_sample_.simple_label_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usando_o_atributo_for","title":"Usando o atributo \"for\"","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\" style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans',sans-serif; line-height: 23.3333px;\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>User<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Click me<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>User<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Name<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Usando o atributo &quot;for&quot;\" id=\"frame_using_the_.22for.22_attribute\" width=\"200\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label/_sample_.using_the_.22for.22_attribute.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/forms.html#the-label-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;label&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/forms.html#the-label-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;label&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/interact/forms.html#h-17.9.1\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;label&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notes","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"click_events_in_nested_<label>_elements\">Click events in nested <code>&lt;label&gt;</code> elements</h4>\n\n<p>Starting with Gecko 8.0 (Firefox 8.0 / Thunderbird 8.0 / SeaMonkey 2.5), a bubbling click event triggers at most one <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>, and the synthetic click event cannot trigger additional <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>s. In Gecko, a click event will still bubble up past a <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>, while in WebKit or Internet Explorer the click event will stop at the <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>. The behavior prior to Gecko 8.0 (triggering multiple <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>s) caused Firefox to stop responding (see <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=646157\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;646157</a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Other form-related elements: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist\"><code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/legend\"><code>&lt;legend&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/optgroup\"><code>&lt;optgroup&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a> and <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect5\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"resumo"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Um elemento HTML <label> representa uma legenda para um item em uma interface de usuário. Ele pode estar associado com um elemento de controle, colocando este dentro do elemento label, ou usando o atributo for. Tal controle é chamado o controle etiquetado do elemento etiqueta. Um input pode ser associado a diversas etiquetas (<label>s).","popularity":0.0036,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<label>: The Input Label element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<label>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<label>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<label>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<label>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<label>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<label>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/label","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/label/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label","title":"<label>"}],"pageTitle":"<label> - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}